1. enable tailscale funnel in tailscale admin

1. enable tailscale funnel in clementi to point to nginx-proxy-manager

    ``` bash
    sudo tailscale funnel --bg 80
    ```

1. generate tailscale certificate in clementi

    ``` bash
    sudo tailscale cert <tailscale_magicdns_hostname>
    ```
1. add generated certificate to nginx-proxy-manager

1. modify n8n docker compose with <tailscale_magicdns_hostname>